text: Nettleton is an unincorporated community in Caldwell County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Nettleton was established in 1872, and remained in operation until 1980. The community was named after George H. Nettleton, a railroad man. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Caldwell County, Missouri Category:1872 establishments in Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Nettleton, Missouri
